 this ultrametric\nstructure by studying the connection of the $\\theta --> -\\infty$ background to\nlittle string theory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Aug 2013 20:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 13 Oct 2013 22:52:56 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 14 Apr 2014 06:58:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
