ied method, we derive a bound on the\nexcess risk of $s$-sparse convex aggregation improving that of Lounici [Math.\nMethods Statist. 16 (2007) 246-259] and providing the optimal rate.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Aug 2013 01:05:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 30 Jun 2017 13:21:04 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 3 Jul 2017 13:29:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-04"}
