_{1}, \\ldots, \\zeta_{n}$ with $\\zeta_{1} + \\cdots + \\zeta_{n} =\n0$. We note that these results do not extend to general finite metric spaces.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Aug 2013 05:52:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 23 Sep 2014 18:00:05 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 16 Jan 2015 21:46:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-01-20"}
